name: DOGMI Coin
description: DOGMI is the first Dog meme coin launched on the Internet Computer Protocol - DOGS GMI! DOGMI, currently under the EXT standard, was developed with a burning system that ensures that every transfer burns 1 DOGMI. An increasingly popular meme coin on the Internet Computer, DOGMI can now be used for tipping on DSCVR - a decentralized social media running on the Internet Computer Protocol.
